data.description: Fantastic all brick ranch with amazing back yard! This 3 bedroom 2 full bath home is ready to move into. Whether you are a first time home buyer or looking to downsize, this is perfect for you! located in a quite cul-de-sac, you'll notice the mature trees that give the front of this house plenty of shade and privacy. Walk through the font door and into a large living room complete with newly refinished hardwood floors and a huge front window that gives way to the tiled kitchen with white cabinets and new stainless steel appliances. This home features a large finished basement with full bathroom, upgraded light fixtures, New HVAC system, New and upgraded electrical panel box and more! The fully fenced in back yard has a large patio, new above ground swimming pool, and a large shed for extra storage. Close to restaurants, shopping, parks, night life, family activities and interstates, this is a must see home in this price point!
